{"questionId":"22584716","questionHtml":"<p>Determine the formula for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>T</mi><mi>k</mi></msub></math> in the form&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>a</mi><msup><mi>k</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><mi>k</mi></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><strong>EITHER</strong><br>attempt to use arithmetic series formula&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>OR</strong><br>attempt to set up simultaneous equations&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong><em>(M1)</em></strong></p>\n<p><strong>OR</strong><br>attempt to use quadratic regression&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced><mrow><msub><mi>T</mi><mi>k</mi></msub><mo>=</mo></mrow></mfenced><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msup><mi>k</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi>k</mi></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; A1A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Note: </strong>Condone variable change (eg in quadratic regression).</p>\n<p>Accept&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mi>b</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\"><em><strong>[3 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"22584716","referenceCode":"24M.2.AHL.TZ2.6aii","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Determine the formula for Tk in the form ak2+bk.","paper":"2","level":"AHL","questionNumber":"ii","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 3]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 1—Number and algebra","Topic 1—Number and algebra","SL 1.2—Arithmetic sequences and series"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}